            [
                "Middle East"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "Kendrick was put in charge of the reorganization of the new division of Textiles at the V&A, part of a total renovation of the Museum, which reopened in 1909.": [],
    "He built the Museum's fibers collection into one of the outstanding ones in the world.": [],
    "Together with C. E. T. Tattersall, he authored the standard <em>Handwoven Carpets</em> in 1922.": [
